FunOnFun

Purpose

This package does multivariate functional Principal Component Analysis (MFPCA) and then conducts function on function regression the MFPCA scores.

  • The URL to the GitHub
  • The URL to the Website

Installation

You can install the development version of FunOnFun from GitHub with:

# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("bpark67/FunOnFun")

Dependencies

This package depends on magrittr, dplyr, purrr, tsibble, tibble, brolgar.
